6. Planned changes to improve safety.

Safety improvement is an on-going process at the facility. Periodic evaluations are performed to assess the maintenance of safe conditions. The facility has been evaluated for necessary upgrades to meet compliance with the 1999 K61.1 ANSI Code and upgrades will be completed in the near future.
